im famous, but they have also made him the prime target of anti-technology extremists who will do whatever it takes to stop him. However, in their attempt to destroy Will, they inadvertently become the catalyst for him to succeed-to be a participant in his own transcendence. For his wife Evelyn (Rebecca Hall) and best friend Max Waters (Paul Bettany), both fellow researchers, the question is not if they can...but if they should. Their worst fears are realized as Will's thirst for knowledge evolves into a seemingly omnipresent quest for power, to what end is unknown. The only thing that is becoming terrifyingly clear is there may be no way to stop him.(C) Warner\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177031_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177031_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177031_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177031_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Johnny Depp\",\"id\":\"162652817\",\"characters\":[\"Dr. Will Caster\"]},{\"name\":\"Paul Bettany\",\"id\":\"162660360\",\"characters\":[\"Max Waters\"]},{\"name\":\"Rebecca Hall\",\"id\":\"355028248\",\"characters\":[\"Evelyn\"]},{\"name\":\"Morgan Freeman\",\"id\":\"162652224\",\"characters\":[\"Joseph Tagger\"]},{\"name\":\"Kate Mara\",\"id\":\"414200709\",\"characters\":[\"Bree\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2209764\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771323313.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/transcendence_2014/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771323313/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771323313/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771323313/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771323313/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771354305\",\"title\":\"A Haunted House 2\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"R\",\"runtime\":87,\"critics_consensus\":\"Sloppy, vulgar, and manic, A Haunted House 2 might be worth a chuckle or two, but mostly it's a string of pop culture references and crude gags that fail to hit their intended targets.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-18\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Rotten\",\"critics_score\":9,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":61},\"synopsis\":\"Crossing new lines and breaking old barriers, A HAUNTED HOUSE 2 is the sequel to the hilarious box-office hit starring Marlon Wayans as Malcolm who, after exorcising the demons of his ex, is starting fresh with his new girlfriend and her two children. After moving into their dream home, Malcolm is once again plagued by bizarre paranormal events. With spine-tingling tension and hilarious punch-lines A HAUNTED HOUSE 2 is inspired by the latest supernatural horror movie franchises and shows that this time... it's not just the house that's haunted! (c) Open Road\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177564_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177564_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177564_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177564_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Marlon Wayans\",\"id\":\"162682781\",\"characters\":[\"Malcolm\"]},{\"name\":\"Jaime Pressly\",\"id\":\"162709861\",\"characters\":[\"Megan\"]},{\"name\":\"Gabriel Iglesias\",\"id\":\"770761504\",\"characters\":[\"Miguel\"]},{\"name\":\"Dave Sheridan\",\"id\":\"162679469\",\"characters\":[\"Aghoul\"]},{\"name\":\"Essence Atkins\",\"id\":\"162711817\",\"characters\":[\"Kisha\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2828996\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771354305.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_haunted_house_2/\",\"cast\":\"htt