ce of a man fighting to salvage all that is important to him.(C) a24\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/66/11176686_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/66/11176686_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/66/11176686_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/66/11176686_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Ben Daniels\",\"id\":\"162654706\"},{\"name\":\"Andrew Scott\",\"id\":\"586476044\"},{\"name\":\"Tom Hardy\",\"id\":\"391527059\",\"characters\":[\"Ivan Locke\"]},{\"name\":\"Olivia Colman\",\"id\":\"770742631\"},{\"name\":\"Bill Milner\",\"id\":\"528392141\"}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2692904\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771357110.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/locke/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771357110/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771357110/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771357110/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771357110/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771352963\",\"title\":\"The Quiet Ones\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG-13\",\"runtime\":98,\"critics_consensus\":\"While it definitely sports a few palpable scares, The Quiet Ones finds Hammer Films trading too heavily on past glories.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-25\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Rotten\",\"critics_score\":39,\"audience_rating\":\"Spilled\",\"audience_score\":38},\"synopsis\":\"From the producer who brought you The Woman In Black and Let Me In comes the unnerving tale of The Quiet Ones. Tucked away in an estate outside of London, Professor Coupland along with a team of university students conduct an \\\"experiment\\\" on Jane Harper, a young girl who harbors unspeakable secrets. What dark forces th