tational artwork is frequently associated with Gonzo journalist Hunter S. Thompson thanks to such books as Fear and Loathing in Las Vegas and The Curse of Lono. A look back at Steadman's remarkable career offers a glimpse into his vivid imagination as interviews with Johnny Depp, Terry Gilliam, Richard E. Grant, Tim Robbins and others offer insight into the man behind the legend. Meanwhile, Steadman watches as his drawings are brought to life through the magic of animation for the very first time. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/62/11176222_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/62/11176222_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/62/11176222_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/62/11176222_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Ralph Steadman\",\"id\":\"770774151\"},{\"name\":\"Johnny Depp\",\"id\":\"162652817\"},{\"name\":\"Terry Gilliam\",\"id\":\"162653515\"},{\"name\":\"Bruce Robinson\",\"id\":\"162670116\"},{\"name\":\"Patrick Godfrey\",\"id\":\"436171788\"}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2112152\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771318182.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/no_good_reason/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771318182/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771318182/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771318182/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771318182/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771355797\",\"title\":\"Walking With The Enemy\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG-13\",\"runtime\":126,\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-25\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Rotten\",\"critics_score\":32,\"audience_rating\":\"Spilled\",\"audience_score\":43},\"synopsis\":\"Inspired by a true story, WALKING WITH THE ENEMY is an unforgettable film of love, courage, and sacrifice. Set in Hungary during the final months of World War ll, a young man sets out to find his displaced family by stealing a Nazi uniform to pose as an officer. Filled with suspense and danger, he undertakes extraordinary measures to reroute his family and other Jews to safety by disrupting the activities of the German occupiers. (c) Liberty Studios\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177583_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177583_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177583_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177583_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Jonas Armstrong\",\"id\":\"770796908\",\"characters\":[\"Elek Cohen\"]},{\"name\":\"Hannah Tointon\",\"id\":\"770920654\",\"characters\":[\"Hannah Schoen\"]},{\"name\":\"Ben Kingsley\",\"id\":\"162653703\",\"characters\":[\"Regent Horthy\"]},{\"name\":\"Simon Dutton\",\"id\":\"770704926\",\"characters\":[\"Miklos Schoen\"]},{\"name\":\"William Hope\",\"id\":\"636150773\",\"characters\":[\"Carl Lutz\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"1515208\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355797.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/walking_with_the_enemy/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355797/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355797/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355797/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355797/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771371304\",\"title\":\"From The Rough\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG\",\"runtime\":97,\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-25\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_score\":-1,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":78},\"synopsis\":\"From the Rough, starring Academy Award nominees Taraji P. Henson and Michael Clarke Duncan and Tom Felton, is the inspirational true story of Catana Starks from historically black university Tennessee State, who became the first African-American woman ever to coach an all-men's team at the collegiate level. Through grit and determination, she overcame incredible odds and deep-seated prejudice from all corners to guide a rag-tag group of golfers to an all-time record championship season. (c) Official Site\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177517_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177517_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177517_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177517_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Taraji P. Henson\",\"id\":\"598455133\"},{\"name\":\"Michael Clarke Duncan\",\"id\":\"162669487\"},{\"name\":\"Tom Felton\",\"id\":\"400215238\"},{\"name\":\"Letoya Luckett\",\"id\":\"770851255\"},{\"name\":\"Henry Simmons\",\"id\":\"364636328\"}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"1704586\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771371304.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/from_the_rough_2014/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771371304/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771371304/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771371304/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771371304/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771355959\",\"title\":\"The German Doctor\",\"year\":2013,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG-13\",\"runtime\":93,\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-25\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Fresh\",\"critics_score\":73,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":67},\"synopsis\":\"Patagonia, 1960. A German doctor (Alex Brendemuhl) meets an Argentinean family and follows them on a long desert road to a small town where the family will be starting a new life. Eva (Natalia Oreiro), Enzo (Diego Peretti) and their three children welcome the doctor into their home and entrust their young daughter, Lilith (Florencia Bado), to his care, not knowing that they are harboring one of the most dangerous criminals in the world. At the same time, Israeli agents are desperately looking to bring THE GERMAN DOCTOR to justice. Based on filmmaker Lucia Puenzo's (XXY) fifth novel, the story follows Josef Mengele, the \\\"Angel of Death,\\\" a German SS officer and a physician at the Auschwitz concentration camp, in the years he spent \\\"hiding\\\", along with many other Nazi's, in South America following his escape from Germany. Mengele was considered to be one of WWII's most heinous Nazi war criminals. (c) Samuel Goldwyn\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/60/11176071_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/60/11176071_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/60/11176071_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/60/11176071_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Alex Brendemuhl\",\"id\":\"385330906\",\"characters\":[\"Mengele\"]},{\"name\":\"Florencia Bado\",\"id\":\"771447491\",\"characters\":[\"Lilith\"]},{\"name\":\"Diego Peretti\",\"id\":\"364647481\",\"characters\":[\"Enzo\"]},{\"name\":\"Natalia Oreiro\",\"id\":\"247606590\",\"characters\":[\"Eva\"]},{\"name\":\"Alan Daicz\",\"id\":\"771444832\",\"characters\":[\"Tomas\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"1847746\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355959.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_german_doctor/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355959/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355959/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355959/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355959/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771325077\",\"title\":\"Who Is Dayani Cristal?\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"Unrated\",\"runtime\":85,\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-25\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Fresh\",\"critics_score\":67,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":100},\"synopsis\":\"The body of an unidentified immigrant is found in the Arizona Desert. In an attempt to retrace his path and discover his story, director Marc Silver and Gael Garcia Bernal embed themselves among migrant travelers on their own mission to cross the border, providing rare insight into the human stories which are so often ignored in the immigration debate. (c) Kino Lorber\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176873_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176873_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176873_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176873_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Gael Garcia Bernal\",\"id\":\"162684026\"}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"1847750\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771325077.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/who_is_dayani_cristal_2013/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771325077/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771325077/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771325077/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771325077/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771374578\",\"title\":\"Next Goal Wins\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"Unrated\",\"runtime\":97,\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-25\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_score\":-1,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":100},\"synopsis\":\"IN 2001, THE TINY PACIFIC ISLAND OF AMERICAN SAMOA SUFFERED A WORLD RECORD 31-0 DEFEAT AT THE HANDS OF AUSTRALIA, GARNERING HEADLINES ACROSS THE WORLD AS THE WORST FOOTBALL TEAM ON THE PLANET. A DECADE AFTER THAT HUMILIATING NIGHT, THEY REMAIN ROOTED TO THE BOTTOM OF FIFA'S WORLD RANKINGS, HAVING SCORED ONLY TWICE IN SEVENTEEN YEARS. THEY HAVE LOST EVERY COMPETITIVE GAME THEY HAVE EVER PLAYED. AGAINST THIS BACKDROP OF SERIAL UNDERACHIEVEMENT, THE TEAM FACE THE DAUNTING PROSPECT OF A QUALIFICATION CAMPAIGN FOR THE UPCOMING 2014 WORLD CUP IN BRAZIL. IT WOULD TAKE A MIRACLE-MAKER OR A MADMAN TO TURN THE TEAM'S FORTUNES AROUND - AND IN MAVERICK DUTCH COACH THOMAS RONGEN THE ISLANDERS SOMEHOW FIND BOTH. AS A LOAN APPOINTMENT FROM THE MIGHTY U.S. SOCCER FEDERATION, WITH EXPERIENCE OF PLAYING ALONGSIDE FOOTBALL GREATS LIKE GEORGE BEST AND JOHANN CRUYFF, RONGEN IS COMPLETELY UNPREPARED FOR WHAT GREETS HIM ON THE ISLAND - IN HIS OWN WORDS IT IS \\\"BY FAR THE LOWEST STANDARD\\\" OF FOOTBALL HE'S EVER SEEN, WITH ONLY HALF OF HIS TEAM EVEN FIT ENOUGH TO PLAY A WHOLE GAME. A LACK OF ATHLETICISM TO ONE SIDE, THOMAS' AILING SQUAD CONTAINS THE EMOTIONALLY SCARRED GOALKEEPER WHO CONCEDED 31 GOALS AGAINST AUSTRALIA A DECADE EARLIER AND A MEMBER OF SAMOA'S THIRD GENDER, THE FA'FAFINE, WHO LIVES 24/7 AS A WOMAN. TO COMPLICATE MATTERS FURTHER THE TEAM'S BEST PLAYER HAS BEEN POSTED 6000 MILES AWAY BY THE US MILITARY. WITH THE TEAM ABOUT TO EMBARK ON A GRUELLING WORLD CUP QUALIFICATION CAMPAIGN, RONGEN HAS JUST ONE MONTH TO TRANSFORM THIS RAGTAG OF LOSERS INTO A WINNING TEAM - AND PERHAPS LEARN A LITTLE ABOUT HIMSELF ALONG THE WAY.(c) Official Site\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177526_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177526_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177526_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177526_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Thomas Rongen\",\"id\":\"771483243\",\"characters\":[\"Head Coach\"]},{\"name\":\"Jaiyah Saelua\",\"id\":\"771487987\",\"characters\":[\"Defender\"]},{\"name\":\"Nicky Salapu\",\"id\":\"771487988\",\"characters\":[\"Goal Keeper\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2446600\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771374578.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/next_goal_wins/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771374578/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771374578/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771374578/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771374578/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771377091\",\"title\":\"Belleville\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"Unrated\",\"runtime\":92,\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-22\",\"dvd\":\"2014-10-15\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_score\":-1,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":99},\"synopsis\":\"Reclusive farmer Willie (Tim O'Leary) has been depressed since the death of his wife Jana (Kate Barton) ten years ago. His only friend is a neighbor named Arlene (Cooper Shaw) who also likes to wallow in misery. Willie's life changes when a stranger from another world named Neila (Ted Trent) shows up on his farm. Over the course of a week, Neila has a profound impact on Willie -- and the entire community of Southern Illinois.(C) Official Site\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/72/11177221_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/72/11177221_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/72/11177221_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/72/11177221_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_c