\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771312513/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771312513/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771305205\",\"title\":\"Rio 2\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"G\",\"runtime\":101,\"critics_consensus\":\"Like most sequels, Rio 2 takes its predecessor's basic template and tries to make it bigger -- which means it's even busier, more colorful, and ultimately more exhausting for viewers outside the youthful target demographic.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-11\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Rotten\",\"critics_score\":47,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":68},\"synopsis\":\"It's a jungle out there for Blu, Jewel and their three kids in RIO 2, after they're hurtled from that magical city to the wilds of the Amazon. As Blu tries to fit in, he goes beak-to-beak with the vengeful Nigel, and meets the most fearsome adversary of all - his father-in-law. All our favorite RIO characters are back, and they're joined by Oscar (R) nominee Andy Garcia, Grammy (R) winner Bruno Mars, Tony (R) winner Kristin Chenoweth and Oscar/Emmy (R)/Tony winner Rita Moreno. RIO 2 also features new Brazilian artists and original music by Janelle Monae and Wondaland. (c) Fox\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177081_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177081_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177081_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177081_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Anne Hathaway\",\"id\":\"162656190\",\"characters\":[\"Jewel\"]},{\"name\":\"Jesse Eisenberg\",\"id\":\"162654393\",\"characters\":[\"Blu\"]},{\"name\":\"will.i.am\",\"id\":\"770877658\",\"characters\":[\"Pedro\"]},{\"name\":\"Jamie Foxx\",\"id\":\"162652975\",\"characters\":[\"Nico\"]},{\"name\":\"George Lopez\",\"id\":\"162652717\",\"characters\":[\"Raphael\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2357291\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771305205.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/rio_2/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771305205/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771305205/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771305205/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771305205/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771323313\",\"title\":\"Transcendence\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG-13\",\"runtime\":119,\"critics_consensus\":\"In his directorial debut, ace cinematographer Wally Pfister remains a distinctive visual stylist, but Transcendence's thought-provoking themes exceed the movie's narrative grasp.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-18\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Rotten\",\"critics_score\":18,\"audience_rating\":\"Spilled\",\"audience_score\":45},\"synopsis\":\"Sci-Fi Thriller. Dr. Will Caster (Johnny Depp) is the foremost researcher in the field of Artificial Intelligence, working to create a sentient machine that combines the collective intelligence of everything ever known with the full range of human emotions. His highly controversial experiments have made him famous, but they have also made him the prime target of anti-technology extremists who will do whatever it takes to stop him. However, in their attempt to destroy Will, they inadvertently become the catalyst for him to succeed-to be a participant in his own transcendence. For his wife Evelyn (Rebecca Hall) and best friend Max Waters (Paul Bettany), both fellow researchers, the question is not if they can...but if they should. Their worst fears are realized as Will's thirst for knowledge evolves into a seemingly omnipresent quest for power, to what end is unknown. The only thing that is becoming terrifyingly clear is there may be no way to stop him.(C) Warner\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177031_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177031_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177031_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/70/11177031_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Johnny Depp\",\"id\":\"162652817\",\"characters\":[\"Dr. Will Caster\"]},{\"name\":\"Paul Bettany\",\"id\":\"162660360\",\"characters\":[\"Max Waters\"]},{\"name\":\"Rebecca Hall\",\"id\":\"355028248\",\"characters\":[\"Evelyn\"]},{\"name\":\"Morgan Freeman\",\"id\":\"162652224\",\"characters\":[\"Joseph Tagger\"]},{\"name\":\"Kate Mara\",\"id\":\"414200709\",\"characters\":[\"Bree\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2209764\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771323313.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/transcendence_2014/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771323313/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771323313/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771323313/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771323313/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771355185\",\"title\":\"Heaven Is for Real\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG\",\"runtime\":100,\"critics_consensus\":\"Heaven Is for Real boasts a well-written screenplay and a talented cast, but overextends itself with heavy-handed sequences depicting concepts it could have trusted the audience to take on faith.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-16\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Rotten\",\"critics_score\":49,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":77},\"synopsis\":\"Based on the #1 New York Times best-selling book of the same name, HEAVEN IS FOR REAL brings to the screen the true story of a small-town father who must find the courage and conviction to share his son's extraordinary, life-changing experience with the world. The film stars Academy Award (R) nominee and Emmy (R) award winning actor Greg Kinnear as Todd Burpo and co-stars Kelly Reilly as Sonja Burpo, the real-life couple whose son Colton (newcomer Connor Corum) claims to have visited Heaven during a near death experience. Colton recounts the details of his amazing journey with childlike innocence and speaks matter-of-factly about things that happened before his birth ... things he couldn't possibly know. Todd and his family are then challenged to examine the meaning from this remarkable event. (c) Sony\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/47/11174759_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/47/11174759_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/47/11174759_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/47/11174759_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Greg Kinnear\",\"id\":\"162652891\",\"characters\":[\"Todd Burpo\"]},{\"name\":\"Kelly Reilly\",\"id\":\"162684910\",\"characters\":[\"Sonja Burpo\"]},{\"name\":\"Connor Corum\",\"id\":\"771472939\",\"characters\":[\"Colton Burpo\"]},{\"name\":\"Margo Martindale\",\"id\":\"542897020\",\"characters\":[\"Nancy Rawling\"]},{\"name\":\"Thomas Haden Church\",\"id\":\"162683650\",\"characters\":[\"Jay Wilkins\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"1929263\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355185.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/heaven_is_for_real/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355185/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355185/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355185/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771355185/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771354305\",\"title\":\"A Haunted House 2\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"R\",\"runtime\":87,\"critics_consensus\":\"Sloppy, vulgar, and manic, A Haunted House 2 might be worth a chuckle or two, but mostly it's a string of pop culture references and crude gags that fail to hit their intended targets.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-18\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Rotten\",\"critics_score\":9,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":61},\"synopsis\":\"Crossing new lines and breaking old barriers, A HAUNTED HOUSE 2 is the sequel to the hilarious box-office hit starring Marlon Wayans as Malcolm who, after exorcising the demons of his ex, is starting fresh with his new girlfriend and her two children. After moving into their dream home, Malcolm is once again plagued by bizarre paranormal events. With spine-tingling tension and hilarious punch-lines A HAUNTED HOUSE 2 is inspired by the latest supernatural horror movie franchises and shows that this time... it's not just the house that's haunted! (c) Open Road\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177564_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177564_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177564_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/17/75/11177564_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Marlon Wayans\",\"id\":\"162682781\",\"characters\":[\"Malcolm\"]},{\"name\":\"Jaime Pressly\",\"id\":\"162709861\",\"characters\":[\"Megan\"]},{\"name\":\"Gabriel Iglesias\",\"id\":\"770761504\",\"characters\":[\"Miguel\"]},{\"name\":\"Dave Sheridan\",\"id\":\"162679469\",\"characters\":[\"Aghoul\"]},{\"name\":\"Essence Atkins\",\"id\":\"162711817\",\"characters\":[\"Kisha\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2828996\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771354305.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_haunted_house_2/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771354305/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771354305/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771354305/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771354305/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771356814\",\"title\":\"Draft Day\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG-13\",\"runtime\":110,\"critics_consensus\":\"It's perfectly pleasant for sports buffs and Costner fans, but overall, Draft Day lives down to its title by relying too heavily on the sort of by-the-numbers storytelling that only a statistician could love.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-11\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Fresh\",\"critics_score\":62,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":72},\"synopsis\":\"On the day of the NFL Draft, general manager Sonny Weaver (Costner) has the opportunity to save football in Cleveland when he trades for the number one pick. He must quickly decide what he's willing to sacrifice in pursuit of perfection as the lines between his personal and professional life become blurred on a life-changing day for a few hundred young men with dreams of playing in the NFL. (c) Lionsgate\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/60/11176039_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/60/11176039_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/60/11176039_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/60/11176039_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Kevin Costner\",\"id\":\"162662350\",\"characters\":[\"Sonny Weaver Jr.\"]},{\"name\":\"Jennifer Garner\",\"id\":\"162660749\",\"characters\":[\"Ali\"]},{\"name\":\"Denis Leary\",\"id\":\"162659182\",\"characters\":[\"Coach Penn\"]},{\"name\":\"Ellen Burstyn\",\"id\":\"162660525\",\"characters\":[\"Barb Weaver\"]},{\"name\":\"Frank Langella\",\"id\":\"162664308\",\"characters\":[\"Anthony Molina\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2223990\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771356814.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/draft_day/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771356814/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771356814/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771356814/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771356814/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771315918\",\"title\":\"Divergent\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG-13\",\"runtime\":140,\"critics_consensus\":\"With an adherence to YA formula that undercuts its individualistic message, Divergent opens its planned trilogy in disappointingly predictable fashion.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-03-21\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Rotten\",\"critics_score\":40,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":77},\"synopsis\":\"DIVERGENT is a thrilling action-adventure film set in a world where people are divided into distinct factions based on human virtues. Tris Prior (Shailene Woodley) is warned she is Divergent and will never fit into any one group. When she discovers a conspiracy by a faction leader (Kate Winslet) to destroy all Divergents, Tris must learn to trust in the mysterious Four (Theo James) and together they must find out what makes being Divergent so dangerous before it's too late. Based on the best-selling book series by Veronica Roth. (C) Summit\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/46/11174665_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/46/11174665_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/46/11174665_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/46/11174665_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Shailene Woodley\",\"id\":\"770676364\",\"characters\":[\"Tris Prior\"]},{\"name\":\"Theo James\",\"id\":\"771083872\",\"characters\":[\"Four\"]},{\"name\":\"Kate Winslet\",\"id\":\"162659302\",\"characters\":[\"Jeanine Matthews\"]},{\"name\":\"Ansel Elgort\",\"id\":\"771409061\",\"characters\":[\"Caleb\"]},{\"name\":\"Ray Stevenson\",\"id\":\"432539848\",\"characters\":[\"Marcus\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"1840309\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771315918.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/divergent/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771315918/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771315918/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771315918/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771315918/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771362204\",\"title\":\"Oculus\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"R\",\"runtime\":105,\"critics_consensus\":\"With an emphasis on dread over gore and an ending that leaves the door wide open for sequels, Oculus could be just the first spine-tingling chapter in a new franchise for discerning horror fans.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-11\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Fresh\",\"critics_score\":72,\"audience_rating\":\"Spilled\",\"audience_score\":54},\"synopsis\":\"Ten years ago, tragedy struck the Russell family, leaving the lives of teenage siblings Tim and Kaylie forever changed when Tim was convicted of the brutal murder of their parents. Now in his 20s, Tim is newly released from protective custody and only wants to move on with his life; but Kaylie, still haunted by that fateful night, is convinced her parents' deaths were caused by something else altogether: a malevolent supernatural force unleashed through the Lasser Glass, an antique mirror in their childhood home. Determined to prove Tim's innocence, Kaylie tracks down the mirror, only to learn similar deaths have befallen previous owners over the past century. With the mysterious entity now back in their hands, Tim and Kaylie soon find their hold on reality shattered by terrifying hallucinations, and realize, too late, that their childhood nightmare is beginning again... (c) Relativity\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176883_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176883_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176883_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176883_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Karen Gillan\",\"id\":\"770875036\",\"characters\":[\"Kaylie Russell\"]},{\"name\":\"Brenton Thwaites\",\"id\":\"771420717\",\"characters\":[\"Tim Russell\"]},{\"name\":\"Rory Cochrane\",\"id\":\"162696268\",\"characters\":[\"Alan Russell\"]},{\"name\":\"Katee Sackhoff\",\"id\":\"459518520\",\"characters\":[\"Marie Russell\"]},{\"name\":\"James Lafferty\",\"id\":\"580188775\",\"characters\":[\"Michael Dumont\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2388715\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771362204.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/oculus/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771362204/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771362204/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771362204/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771362204/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771318848\",\"title\":\"Bears\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"G\",\"runtime\":77,\"critics_consensus\":\"Sweet, beautifully filmed, and admirably short on sugarcoating, Bears continues Disneynature's winning streak.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-04-18\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Certified Fresh\",\"critics_score\":90,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":83},\"synopsis\":\"In an epic story of breathtaking scale, Disneynature's new True Life Adventure \\\"Bears\\\" showcases a year in the life of a bear family as two impressionable young cubs are taught life's most important lessons. Set against a majestic Alaskan backdrop teeming with life, their journey begins as winter comes to an end and the bears emerge from hibernation to face the bitter cold. The world outside is exciting-but risky-as the cubs' playful descent down the mountain carries with it a looming threat of avalanches. As the season changes from spring to summer, the brown bears must work hard to find food-ultimately feasting at a plentiful salmon run-while staying safe from rival male bears and predators, including an ever-present wolf pack. \\\"Bears\\\" captures the fast-moving action and suspense of life in one of the planet's last great wildernesses-Alaska! Directed by Alastair Fothergill (\\\"Earth,\\\" \\\"African Cats\\\" and \\\"Chimpanzee\\\") and Keith Scholey (\\\"African Cats\\\"), \\\"Bears\\\" arrives in theaters April 18, 2014, to celebrate Earth Day.(c) Disney\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/29/11172983_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/29/11172983_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/29/11172983_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/29/11172983_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"John C. Reilly\",\"id\":\"162652855\",\"characters\":[\"Narrator\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2458776\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771318848.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bears_2014/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771318848/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771318848/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771318848/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771318848/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771371948\",\"title\":\"God's Not Dead\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG\",\"runtime\":95,\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-03-21\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Rotten\",\"critics_score\":13,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":86},\"synopsis\":\"Present-day college freshman and devout Christian, Josh Wheaton (Shane Harper), finds his faith challenged on his first day of Philosophy class by the dogmatic and argumentative Professor Radisson (Kevin Sorbo). Radisson begins class by informing students that they will need to disavow, in writing, the existence of God on that first day, or face a failing grade. As other students in the class begin scribbling the words \\\"God Is Dead\\\" on pieces of paper as instructed, Josh find himself at a crossroads, having to choose between his faith and his future. Josh offers a nervous refusal, provoking an irate reaction from his smug professor. Radisson assigns him a daunting task: if Josh will not admit that \\\"God Is Dead,\\\" he must prove God's existence by presenting well-researched, intellectual arguments and evidence over the course of the semester, and engage Radisson in a head-to-head debate in front of the class. If Josh fails to convince his classmates of God's existence, he will fail the course and hinder his lofty academic goals. With almost no one in his corner, Josh wonders if he can really fight for what he believes. Can he actually prove the existence of God? Wouldn't it just be easier just to write \\\"God Is Dead\\\" and put the whole incident behind him? GOD'S NOT DEAD weaves together multiple stories of faith, doubt and disbelief, culminating in a dramatic call to action. The film will educate, entertain, and inspire moviegoers to explore what they really believe about God, igniting important conversations and life-changing decisions. --(C) Official Site\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/59/11175915_mob.png\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/59/11175915_pro.png\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/59/11175915_det.png\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/59/11175915_ori.png\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Shane Harper\",\"id\":\"770846005\",\"characters\":[\"Josh\"]},{\"name\":\"Kevin Sorbo\",\"id\":\"162676109\",\"characters\":[\"Professor Radisson\"]},{\"name\":\"David A.R. White\",\"id\":\"559759203\",\"characters\":[\"Pastor Dave\"]},{\"name\":\"Dean Cain\",\"id\":\"162696548\",\"characters\":[\"Mark\"]},{\"name\":\"Willie Robertson\",\"id\":\"771465246\",\"characters\":[\"Willie Robertson\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2528814\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771371948.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gods_not_dead/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771371948/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771371948/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771371948/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771371948/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771305170\",\"title\":\"Noah\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG-13\",\"runtime\":139,\"critics_consensus\":\"With sweeping visuals grounded by strong performances in service of a timeless tale told on a human scale, Darren Aronofsky's Noah brings the Bible epic into the 21st century.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-03-28\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Certified Fresh\",\"critics_score\":77,\"audience_rating\":\"Spilled\",\"audience_score\":46},\"synopsis\":\"Russell Crowe stars as Noah in the film inspired by the epic story of courage, sacrifice and hope. Directed by visionary filmmaker Darren Aronofsky (c) Paramount\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/69/11176923_mob.png\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/69/11176923_pro.png\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/69/11176923_det.png\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/69/11176923_ori.png\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Russell Crowe\",\"id\":\"162652569\",\"characters\":[\"Noah\"]},{\"name\":\"Jennifer Connelly\",\"id\":\"162652853\",\"characters\":[\"Naameh\"]},{\"name\":\"Ray Winstone\",\"id\":\"162693523\",\"characters\":[\"Tubal Cain\"]},{\"name\":\"Emma Watson\",\"id\":\"162655378\",\"characters\":[\"Il-la\",\"Ila\"]},{\"name\":\"Anthony Hopkins\",\"id\":\"162653967\",\"characters\":[\"Methuselah\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"1959490\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771305170.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/noah_2014/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771305170/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771305170/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771305170/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771305170/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771312437\",\"title\":\"The Grand Budapest Hotel\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"R\",\"runtime\":100,\"critics_consensus\":\"Typically stylish but deceptively thoughtful, The Grand Budapest Hotel finds Wes Anderson once again using ornate visual environments to explore deeply emotional ideas.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-03-07\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Certified Fresh\",\"critics_score\":92,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":89},\"synopsis\":\"THE GRAND BUDAPEST HOTEL recounts the adventures of Gustave H, a legendary concierge at a famous European hotel between the wars, and Zero Moustafa, the lobby boy who becomes his most trusted friend. The story involves the theft and recovery of a priceless Renaissance painting and the battle for an enormous family fortune -- all against the back-drop ofa suddenly and dramatically changing Continent. (c) Fox Searchlight\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/73/11177373_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/73/11177373_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/73/11177373_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/73/11177373_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Saoirse Ronan\",\"id\":\"770680691\",\"characters\":[\"Agatha\"]},{\"name\":\"Ralph Fiennes\",\"id\":\"162653681\",\"characters\":[\"M. Gustave\"]},{\"name\":\"Bill Murray\",\"id\":\"162653064\",\"characters\":[\"M. Ivan\"]},{\"name\":\"Tilda Swinton\",\"id\":\"162654047\",\"characters\":[\"Madame D.\"]},{\"name\":\"Jeff Goldblum\",\"id\":\"162668455\",\"characters\":[\"Deputy Kovacs\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2278388\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771312437.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_grand_budapest_hotel/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771312437/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771312437/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771312437/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771312437/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771321700\",\"title\":\"Muppets Most Wanted\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG\",\"runtime\":112,\"critics_consensus\":\"While it may not reach the delirious heights of The Muppets, Muppets Most Wanted still packs in enough clever gags, catchy songs, and celebrity cameos to satisfy fans of all ages.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-03-21\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Certified Fresh\",\"critics_score\":79,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":66},\"synopsis\":\"Disney's \\\"Muppets Most Wanted\\\" takes the entire Muppets gang on a global tour, selling out grand theaters in some of Europe's most exciting destinations, including Berlin, Madrid, Dublin and London. But mayhem follows the Muppets overseas, as they find themselves unwittingly entangled in an international crime caper headed by Constantine-the World's Number One Criminal and a dead ringer for Kermit the Frog-and his dastardly sidekick Dominic, aka Number Two, portrayed by Ricky Gervais. The film stars Tina Fey as Nadya, a feisty prison guard, and Ty Burrell as Interpol agent Jean Pierre Napoleon.(c) Disney\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176898_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176898_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176898_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/17/68/11176898_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Ricky Gervais\",\"id\":\"378620549\",\"characters\":[\"Dominic aka Number Two\"]},{\"name\":\"Tina Fey\",\"id\":\"427823878\",\"characters\":[\"Nadya\"]},{\"name\":\"Ty Burrell\",\"id\":\"326391544\",\"characters\":[\"Jean Pierre Napoleon\"]},{\"name\":\"Ray Liotta\",\"id\":\"162669095\",\"characters\":[\"Big Papa\"]},{\"name\":\"Steve Whitmire\",\"id\":\"162656592\",\"characters\":[\"Beaker\",\"Foo Foo\",\"Kermit\",\"Link Hogthrob\",\"Lips\",\"Rizzo the Rat\",\"Statler\",\"The Newsman\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"2281587\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771321700.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/muppets_most_wanted/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771321700/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771321700/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771321700/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771321700/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771169232\",\"title\":\"Mr. Peabody & Sherman\",\"year\":2014,\"mpaa_rating\":\"PG\",\"runtime\":92,\"critics_consensus\":\"Mr. Peabody & Sherman offers a surprisingly entertaining burst of colorful all-ages fun, despite its dated source material and rather convoluted plot.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-03-07\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Certified Fresh\",\"critics_score\":79,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":77},\"synopsis\":\"Mr. Peabody, the most accomplished dog in the world, and his mischievous boy Sherman, use their time machine - the WABAC - to go on the most outrageous adventures known to man or dog. But when Sherman takes the WABAC out for a joyride to impress his friend Penny, they accidentally rip a hole in the universe, wreaking havoc on the most important events in world history. Before they forever alter the past, present and future, Mr. Peabody must come to their rescue, ultimately facing the most daunting challenge of any era: figuring out how to be a parent. Together, the time traveling trio will make their mark on history. (c) Fox\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/57/11175779_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/57/11175779_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/57/11175779_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/17/57/11175779_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Ty Burrell\",\"id\":\"326391544\",\"characters\":[\"Mr. Peabody\"]},{\"name\":\"Max Charles\",\"id\":\"771103441\",\"characters\":[\"Sherman\"]},{\"name\":\"Stephen Colbert\",\"id\":\"326397081\",\"characters\":[\"Paul Peterson\"]},{\"name\":\"Allison Janney\",\"id\":\"434230452\",\"characters\":[\"Ms. Grunion\",\"Paula Peterson\"]},{\"name\":\"Ariel Winter\",\"id\":\"770744043\",\"characters\":[\"Penny Peterson\"]}],\"alternate_ids\":{\"imdb\":\"0864835\"},\"links\":{\"self\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771169232.json\",\"alternate\":\"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mr_peabody_and_sherman/\",\"cast\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771169232/cast.json\",\"clips\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771169232/clips.json\",\"reviews\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771169232/reviews.json\",\"similar\":\"http://api.rottentomatoes.com/api/public/v1.0/movies/771169232/similar.json\"}},{\"id\":\"771249085\",\"title\":\"300: Rise of an Empire\",\"year\":2013,\"mpaa_rating\":\"R\",\"runtime\":103,\"critics_consensus\":\"It's bound to hit some viewers as an empty exercise in stylish gore, and despite a gonzo starring performance from Eva Green, 300: Rise of an Empire is a step down from its predecessor.\",\"release_dates\":{\"theater\":\"2014-03-07\"},\"ratings\":{\"critics_rating\":\"Rotten\",\"critics_score\":42,\"audience_rating\":\"Upright\",\"audience_score\":60},\"synopsis\":\"Based on Frank Miller's latest graphic novel Xerxes and told in the breathtaking visual style of the blockbuster \\\"300,\\\" this new chapter of the epic saga takes the action to a fresh battlefield-on the sea-as Greek general Themistokles (Sullivan Stapleton) attempts to unite all of Greece by leading the charge that will change the course of the war. \\\"300: Rise of an Empire\\\" pits Themistokles against the massive invading Persian forces led by mortal-turned-god Xerxes (Rodrigo Santoro), and Artemisia (Eva Green), vengeful commander of the Persian navy. (c) WB\",\"posters\":{\"thumbnail\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/19/11171969_mob.jpg\",\"profile\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/19/11171969_pro.jpg\",\"detailed\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/19/11171969_det.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/17/19/11171969_ori.jpg\"},\"abridged_cast\":[{\"name\":\"Sullivan Stapleton\",\"id\":\"770706605\"